OL,3,C'No watering down of Hillsborough Law'
OL,4,Cahead of first debate
OL,6,FThe courage of campaigners whose lives
OL,7,Fwere devastated by state scandals will
OL,8,Fbe honoured as the so-called
OL,9,FHillsborough Law comes before
OL,10,FParliament for its first debate, the
OL,11,FJustice Secretary has said.
OL,13,FThe Public Office (Accountability)
OL,14,FBill will have its second reading in
OL,15,FParliament on Monday 3 November,
OL,16,Fhaving been formally introduced in the
OL,17,FCommons in September to begin the
OL,18,Fjourney towards becoming law.
