OL,3,C'No watering down of Hillsborough Law'
OL,4,Cahead of first debate
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer had
OL,7,Fpreviously pledged to bring it before
OL,8,FParliament by the 36th anniversary of
OL,9,Fthe tragedy, which was on 15 April,
OL,10,Fbut Downing Street then said more time
OL,11,Fwas needed to redraft it amid concerns
OL,12,Famong some campaigners that the Bill's
OL,13,Fcontents had been diluted and would
OL,14,Fnot include a legal duty of candour.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
