OL,3,C'No watering down of Hillsborough Law'
OL,4,Cahead of first debate
OL,6,FKnown as the Hillsborough Law, the
OL,7,FBill is intended to make sure the
OL,8,Fauthorities will face criminal
OL,9,Fsanctions if they attempt to cover up
OL,10,Fthe facts behind disasters such as the
OL,11,F1989 Hillsborough tragedy or the 2017
OL,12,FGrenfell Tower fire.
OL,14,FAhead of Monday's debate, David Lammy
OL,15,F` who is also deputy prime minister `
OL,16,Fdescribed the Bill as "landmark
OL,17,Flegislation" and paid tribute to the
OL,18,Fdecades of campaigning by the bereaved
OL,19,Fand survivors of major scandals.
OL,26,@xD@WOUyD@LO]
