OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F395A1762196337
OL,3,C'No watering down of Hillsborough Law'
OL,4,Cahead of first debate
OL,6,F"Second Reading is where we start
OL,7,Fhonouring that courage by beginning
OL,8,Fthis Bill's journey through
OL,9,FParliament: to finally place a legal
OL,10,Fduty of candour on all public
OL,11,Fofficials; to give grieving victims
OL,12,Fthe legal help and support they need
OL,13,Fat inquests; and to make clear that
OL,14,Fmisleading the public carries real
OL,15,Fconsequences."
OL,17,FHe pledged to ensure the Bill is
OL,18,Fpassed in its "current, strong form"
OL,19,Fand not "watered down" during its
OL,20,Fpassage through Parliament.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@NO]zD@OOUzD@dO]{D@IOU{D@VO]
