OL,3,C'No watering down of Hillsborough Law'
OL,4,Cahead of first debate
OL,6,FThe Hillsborough disaster led to the
OL,7,Fdeaths of 97 football fans during the
OL,8,FFA Cup semi-final between Liverpool
OL,9,Fand Nottingham Forest at the football
OL,10,Fground in Sheffield.
OL,12,FVictims have previously told how they
OL,13,Fwere "left with no transparency, no
OL,14,Ftruth" only "justice cover-ups and a
OL,15,Fsystem that closes ranks and protects
OL,16,Fthose who we should trust ` ordinary
OL,17,Fpeople that are thrown into an alien
OL,18,Fsystem designed to shield the state
OL,19,Ffrom scrutiny and accountability".
OL,26,@uD@FOUvD@FO]vD@MOU{D@aO]
