OL,3,C'No watering down of Hillsborough Law'
OL,4,Cahead of first debate
OL,6,FSupporters of a duty of candour for
OL,7,Fpublic officials include victims of
OL,8,Fthe Grenfell Tower fire, which killed
OL,9,F72 people, and the Post Office Horizon
OL,10,FIT scandal, which saw hundreds of
OL,11,Fpeople wrongfully prosecuted and
OL,12,Fconvicted.
OL,14,FAmong what the Government has
OL,15,Fpreviously described as the "seismic
OL,16,Fchanges" as part of the Bill, are the
OL,17,Fbiggest expansion of legal aid in a
OL,18,Fdecade for bereaved families, with non-
OL,19,Fmeans tested help and support for
OL,20,Finquests.
OL,26,@wD@]OUxD@HO]
